Titolo: NBA Showdown (video game)

Anno: 1993

Descrizione: NBA Showdown is a 1993 video game for the Super Nintendo Entertainment System game console. The game is a sequel to Bulls vs. Blazers video game. The same title was re-released for the Mega Drive as NBA Showdown 94. It is the fifth and final game in the NBA Playoffs series of games, before the series was re-branded as NBA Live.